Dedication: _Hisbonen!_ is dedicated to the memory of Rav Dov Zemmel z'l, a talmid muvak of R Chayim Pinchas Scheinberg, who taught dozens of talmidim to learn Gemara in an authentic and accurate way. This tool is inspired by the _derech halimud_ he imparted to his talmidim.
